 *rotr-32-7-r1cs-lifted*
 (rotr-32-7-spec (acl2::packbv '32 '1
                               (list |main.in[31]| |main.in[30]|
                                     |main.in[29]| |main.in[28]|
                                     |main.in[27]| |main.in[26]|
                                     |main.in[25]| |main.in[24]|
                                     |main.in[23]| |main.in[22]|
